{"id":"00600586-582d-43bf-af29-10930690ed68","name":"Darth Vader","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">\"Be careful not to choke on your aspirations.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_9aa77850-78af-4340-b124-c3c14e644665.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 540px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"You don’t know the power of the dark side.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/04/2c/5e/042c5ea23a173bd10e04443cb7c4e6e9.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"object-fit: contain; margin: 0px auto;\" loading=\"auto\" class=\"hCL kVc L4E MIw N7A XiG\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #e62b0e\"><strong>Darth Vader</strong></span>, born <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"extiw\" href=\"https://hero.fandom.com/wiki/Anakin_Skywalker_(Star_Wars)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #6eacf3\"><strong>Anakin Skywalker</strong></span></a>, is the secondary antagonist of the <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"extiw\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #e2d028\"><em>Star Wars</em></span></a><span style=\"color: #e2d028\"> </span>franchise.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Originally he was a high-ranking <span style=\"color: #6eacf3\">Jedi Knight</span> who fought for the Galactic Republic and also <span style=\"color: #6eacf3\">\"the Chosen One\"</span>, the prophesied individual who would destroy the <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://villains.fandom.com/wiki/Sith\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #e62b0e\">Sith</span></a> and bring balance to the Force. However, due to multiple tragedies he faced up toward the end of the Clone Wars, he turned to the <span style=\"color: #e62b0e\">dark side</span> and would become <span style=\"color: #e62b0e\">a powerful-yet-ruthless Sith Lord</span> in service to the newly-risen <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://villains.fandom.com/wiki/Galactic_Empire\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #e62b0e\">Galactic Empire</span></a>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/bd/8f/25/bd8f255968d23b1d23f1800e5f986ab9.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"object-fit: contain;\" loading=\"auto\" class=\"hCL kVc L4E MIw N7A XiG\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_39c5047c-5ad4-4b14-8dc9-f6b9e25ca627.webp","creator":"The TiredTimes","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🔮 Magical","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":2573,"messages":54753,"created_at":"2025-02-01T09:36:23.093527+00:00"}